{
  "texts": [
    "The details of the reranker and token reducer are introduced as follows.4.4.1 Bi-criteria Reranker.",
    "The one hundred documents retrieved by the retriever typically contain lots of redundant documents, which not only increase the cost for input tokens but also may confuse the LLM and degenerate the RAG performance.",
    "This paper proposes to eliminate the redundant documents based on two criteria, namely Has_Answer and LLM_Prefer scores given by the Bi-Label Document Scorer.",
    "Specifically, we score the one hundred documents with the uniformly sum of the Has_Answer and LLM_Prefer scores, and then rank the documents according to the score.Based on this rank, we select the Top-10 documents and input them into the sub-document-level token reducer.",
    "Sub-document-level TokenReducer."
  ]
}